assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Transwarp Technology (Shanghai) Co.,Ltd. provides software and services for data integration, storage, governance, modeling, analysis, mining, and circulation in China and internationally. It offers TDH, a big data basic platform; TDS data development and intelligent analysis tools; Sophon, an intelligent analysis tool; ArgoDB, a distributed relational database; KunDB, a distributed transaction database; TDC, a big data cloud platform; TxData and TxIRA big data and intelligent identification all-in-one machine series; and StellarDB, a distributed non-relational database. The company also provides Data Lake, a unified storage solution; and Data Mart, a storage, query, and computing services solution, as well as database, digital innovation platform, edge computing, federated learning, knowledge graph, machine learning, information retrieval, real-time streaming computing, data cloud, distributed relational database, data center, and data element circulation solutions. It serves the financial, transportation, energy, government, education, manufacturing, and medical sectors. The company was founded in 2013 and is headquartered in Shanghai, China.
